title: The Adventure Zone: Graduation Ep. 7 "Secrets, Secrets"
description: It's the end of the semester! The Thundermen meet with some teachers, trick a counselor and look for poison. When the sun goes down, it's party time. For some that means presents and dancing. For others, oaths and secrets. A dream turns into a nightmare and it seems a friend is missing.
author: shows@themcelroy.family (The McElroys)
